(C1) 
					  2
(D1) 				   (x + 1)
(C2) 
				  2
(D2) 				 x  + 2 x + 1
(C3) 

|(C1) FACTOR(x^2+2*x+1);|
(D3) 				     (C1)
(C4) 
$$\left(x+1\right)^2\leqno{\tt (D1)}$$
(D4) 				     (D1)
(C5) 

|(C2) EXPAND(%);|
(D5) 				     (C2)
(C6) 
$$x^2+2\,x+1\leqno{\tt (D2)}$$
(D6) 				     (D2)
(C7) 
